    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1893-05-11T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1893-05-11T00:00:00-05:00" n="699" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d699">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Gresham</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">von Holleben</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1893-05-11">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 11,
                                1893</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The Secretary of State presents his compliments to the minister of
                            Germany, and asks that he will kindly call at the Department to-day at 3
                            o’clock for the purpose of discussing a detail in relation to Samoan
                            matters.</p>
            </div>
